Go Trust Store
==============

Trust-store bindings for Go.


Installation
------------

1. Install the prerequisites:

    $ sudo apt-get install pkg-config libtrust-store1 libdbus-cpp4

2. Install the Go Trust Store bindings:

    $ go get launchpad.net/go-trust-store/...


More Detailed Documentation
---------------------------

Visit https://godoc.org/launchpad.net/go-trust-store/trust
